{"calories":"580","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"There’s a lot of reasons to love rigatoni pasta, but our number 1 reason is its shape. Hollow on the inside and ridged outside, it scoops up and absorbs the maximum amount of sauce possible—what more could you ask for?! This creamy, dreamy, tomato sauce studded with hearty kale and roasted mushrooms is something you’ll want to scoop up as much of as possible. Simple, comforting, and perfect for chilly winter nights, this rigatoni’s one for the ages.","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"6e2ba1d875","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16886/1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16886/menu_small_1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16883/1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16880/1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16880/hero_1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16880/menu_small_1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16880/small_square_1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16880/medium_square_1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16880/recipe_profile_page_1862_Creamy_Tomato_Rigatoni_with_Roasted_Mushrooms_and_Kale_HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Creamy Tomato Rigatoni with Roasted Mushrooms and Kale","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"35-45","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"creamy-tomato-rigatoni-with-roasted-mushrooms-and-kale","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/9310/recipe_card20161212-4-13znl4z.pdf","recipe_id":1862,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Creamy Tomato Rigatoni ","subtitle":"with Roasted Mushrooms and Kale","title":"Creamy Tomato Rigatoni","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did! \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWiping mushrooms clean instead of rinsing prevents them from absorbing water. They won't brown well if they're too wet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile it cooks, pasta will release starches into the boiling water. Adding some reserved pasta water to the sauce will help it bind with the noodles.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","baking sheet","12\" large high-sided pan"],"id":1862,"ingredients":["garlic","basil","dinosaur kale","cremini mushrooms","rigatoni","crushed red pepper","jar tomato purée","heavy cream","grated Parmesan cheese"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"garlic","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"basil","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1276/medium_square_medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"dinosaur kale","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/482/medium_square_DINOSAUR_KALE_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"rigatoni","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1231/medium_square_sfoglini_rigatoni.jpg"},{"name":"crushed red pepper","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/39/medium_square_CRUSHED_RED_PEPPER_copy.jpg"},{"name":"jar tomato purée","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1267/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_ingredients-9.jpg"},{"name":"heavy cream","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/71/medium_square_coconut-milk.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/22/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/15054/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 425°F. Bring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e and roughly tear leaves, discarding stems. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003ekale\u003c/strong\u003e and tear leaves into bite-size pieces, discarding stems. Wipe \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e clean with a damp paper towel and thinly slice (see Recipe Tip).\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast Mushrooms","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/15055/recipe_card_size_2._Roast_Mushrooms.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOn a baking sheet, toss \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms \u003c/strong\u003ewith \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired. Roast until crispy, 10-12 minutes. Set aside.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook Rigatoni ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/15056/recipe_card_size_3._Cook_Rigatoni.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile mushrooms roast, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003erigatoni\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 10 minutes. Reserve \u003cstrong\u003e.5 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e for thickening the sauce, then drain and set aside.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook Marinara Sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/15057/recipe_card_size_4._Cook_Marinara_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile rigatoni cooks, heat \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e in a large high-sided pan over medium heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003egarlic \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003ecrushed red pepper\u003c/strong\u003e. Sauté, stirring, until garlic is golden and fragrant, about 1 minute. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003etomato purée \u003c/strong\u003eand season with \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired. Cook, stirring occasionally, until warmed through, 6-8 minutes.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Wilt Kale ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/15058/recipe_card_size_5._Wilt_Kale.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd kale to pan with marinara sauce over medium heat and stir to wilt, 2-3 minutes. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Season and Plate Rigatoni ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/15059/recipe_card_size_6._Season_Rigatoni.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd\u003cstrong\u003e cream\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003erigatoni\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e to pan with sauce over medium heat and cook, stirring, until warmed through, 1-2 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003ereserved pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, 1 tablespoon at a time, until sauce is thick and clings to noodles (see Recipe Tip). Remove pan from heat, divide pasta between plates, and garnish with \u003cstrong\u003ebasil \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003eremaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e. Dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"\u003c 600 Calories","slug":"low-calorie","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"\u003c 600 Calories","slug":"low-calorie","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}